# ❌⭕ Tic-Tac-Toe Game (C++)

A clean, console-based Tic-Tac-Toe game written in modern C++. This project uses object-oriented design and is built with clarity and modularity in mind.

---

## 🎮 Features

- Two-player gameplay (X vs O)
- Win detection across rows, columns, and diagonals
- Input validation and clean board rendering
- Fully modular with header/source separation

---

## 📦 Coming Soon

- Player name input
- Score tracking and saving via local database
- Match history system

---

## 💻 Tech Stack

- Language: C++20
- STL: `vector`, `iostream`, `string`, `iomanip`
- Clean OOP structure

---

